 <item> <title>On the Path to Opportunity</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/speeches/path-opportunity</link>
 <description>Secretary of Education John B. King, Jr., spoke to the graduating class at Milwaukee Area Technical College (MATC) on May 13, 2016. The Secretary noted that community colleges like MATC are creating paths to opportunity for so many students across the country each day, and he encouraged the graduating class to pay forward the benefit of the higher education they have received by mentoring others and serving their communities.</description>
